<tr>
<th scope="row">Contents</th>
<td class="view" colspan="3"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">This is a new day, starting off the new year of 2012. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><font color="#000000">I hope that you all have a blessed and fruitful new year. <o:p></o:p></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.4pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">I also hope that our society will become even more mature where everyone is considerate of, encourages and edifies one another, filled with love and compassion.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><font color="#000000">This year, we shall build upon the firm foundation for a welfare state that we’ve all been wishing for. In this regard, all the officials of Ministry of Health and Welfare and I myself are recommitting ourselves to achieving this goal with more aggressive eagerness and a new perspective. <o:p></o:p></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.2pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.8pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">It is natural to see various welfare demands arising as the economy grows and different interests of different areas of the society become intertwined with one another in a complex manner. The basic welfare policy challenge will be to respond to such demands of the public with wisdom.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"> We have to ensure mutual understanding through vigorous communication and earn the people’s agreement in setting policy priorities in terms of significance and urgency. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><font color="#000000">More financial resources and efforts shall be invested in areas that require urgent care and support and when it comes to tasks that need long-term resolutions, directions shall be determined and the framework for such tasks shall be firmly built first. <o:p></o:p></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Although it may be highly challenging, we still have to go through such process in order to achieve a true advanced welfare state where there is genuine unity and fair distribution of welfare benefits among different social classes and generations. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">To this end, not only government officials but also all those involved in the health and welfare area shall have a stronger sense of responsibility. Health and welfare policies cannot succeed unless there is trust among the public. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Every single one of those who work in the welfare field including government officials, pharmaceutical and welfare service providers, etc shall make more efforts to receive greater trust and support from the public.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Ministry of Health and Welfare will take up a lead in building a closer relationship with the public based on greater trust.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.2pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.8pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Welfare cannot be achieved with efforts made by the government and public sector only. Participation by the entire people of the nation is needed. Even small acts of care and kindness to one another from nurturing a happy family and workplace to always caring about and sharing with neighbors will all serve as precious contribution to building a welfare state. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Especially, being considerate of the elderly, children, and the challenged in our neighborhoods in everyday lives will work far greater in building a better society than any welfare policies. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 5.7pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; letter-spacing: -0.3pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Ministry of Health and Welfare will press ahead with health and medical policies, social welfare policies as well as policy measures to handle low birth rates and aging population with boldness and consistency on the strength of more active cooperation by the public and policy makers’ stronger sense of responsibility. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">In addition, we will do our best to accomplish tangible results in implementing core policy tasks for new year such as the creation of sustainable health and medical system with focus on prevention, the reinforcement of the social safety net and the operation of more tightly-knitted welfare service supply network as well as the expansion of childcare service, the policy support for post-retirement preparation, etc.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶">Once again, I hope that this New Year will be a greatly blessed year to you all and to our entire nation. </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ±¼¸²"><o:p><font color="#000000"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-indent: 6pt; mso-char-indent-count: .5">
